for the commander-in-chief be the test.

154
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,590
The one elected

155
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,510
will be the president.

156
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,150
That's reasonable.

157
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,230
Recently, Wei Jinghai

158
