189
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:45,550
It's for ourselves.
Just add more filling.

190
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,510
Look, it's coming out again.

191
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,910
You're just here to make trouble for me.

192
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,790
I told you it would come out.

193
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:53,230
Bao.

194
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,710
- Later...
- Uncle.

195
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,190
Ms. Fang.

196
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,590
Bao said you have something

197
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,510
to celebrate.

198
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:02,790
I don't have anything to give you,

199
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,070
so I came to cook you a meal.

200
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:06,070
Alright, then I'm in for a treat.

201
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,110
Thanks, Ms. Fang.

202
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,910
I'll go drop off my bag
and come back to help.

203
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,550
Uncle, have you finished your work?

204
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,510
Yes.

205
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,390
Think about what you want.

206
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,950
When my bonus comes,
I'll buy it for you.

207
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,990
I don't really want anything.

208
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,350
You've been quite diligent lately.

209
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,430
When we moved in,
there was a big footprint.

210
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,990
Where did it go?

211
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,910
I couldn't make it go away.

212
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,590
It's Ms. Fang's work.

213
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,510
Ms. Fang is like a magician.

214
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:42,310
She dipped a towel in white vinegar

215
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,270
and just wiped it like this,

216
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:44,350
and it was gone.

217
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:45,910
And this, and this.

218
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:46,870
Look.

219
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,590
Look at this.

220
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,510
Look at the fridge.

221
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,110
There used to be a big crack, right?

222
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:53,550
Do you know what Ms. Fang used
to fix it?

223
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:54,350
What?

224
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,190
Toothpaste.

225
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:57,870
She just wiped it, and it's gone.

226
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,310
Alright, Bao.

227
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,350
Where did you put the pepper we bought?

228
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:01,990
I know.

229
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,670
I'll get it.

230
00:12:03,880 --> 00:12:05,150
I'll wash my hands and come help.

231
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,270
Alright.

232
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:13,750
This place will be relocated?

233
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,510
They say they're building
a commercial city.

234
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,910
Other merchants have agreed,

235
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,950
but I don't want to move.

236
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,750
Is it because of price?

237
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,350
The price is indeed low.

238
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,510
Not long ago,

239
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,870
my shop was doing well,

240
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,470
so I renovated the gas and drainage.

241
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,670
But they don't recognize that.

242
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,590
The main issue is

243
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,990
that Tongtong needs to go to school,

244
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,790
and there are regular customers here.

245
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,910
I also have a house.

246
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,830
I'm still paying the mortgage.

247
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,550
I really can't handle this.

248
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,990
So, have you talked to them?

249
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,070
What did they say?

250
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,110
Don't mention it.

251
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,390
The developers

252
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,590
come every few days,

253
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,310
but they never talk about anything.

254
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,670
They just ask
if we've made up our minds.

255
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,070
Ms. Fang doesn't want to sign,

256
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,710
so they sit down to eat

257
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,870
and act polite

258
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,990
but never talk about the issue.

259
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:09,910
Besides, those people

260
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:10,990
all look so fierce.

261
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,310
When they sit in my resto...

262
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,510
They don't look like good people.

263
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,990
Anyway, this has got out.

264
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,950
It's already affecting my business
with regular customers.

265
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:23,110
They've been telling other merchants

266
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:25,630
that if I don't sign,

267
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:26,670
this deal will fall through.

268
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,710
Now, other merchants

269
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,070
are coming to cause trouble for me.

270
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:37,870
Oh, no.

271
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,510
There's still water in the pot.

272
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,470
Bao, I'll go.

273
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,910
Don't move. Sit down.

274
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:43,910
You should talk to Uncle.

275
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:44,710
You two talk.

276
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,190
Actually, I've accepted it

277
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:57,470
since it's gotten to this point.

278
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:00,070
A couple of days ago,
I went to check out the shop.

279
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:02,190
The price for a good location

280
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,470
is ridiculously high.

281
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,910
When do they usually come by?

282
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:11,310
They definitely come on weekends.

283
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,750
Then I'll go this weekend

284
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,510
and talk to them.

285
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,430
Uncle,

286
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:23,150
I've been waiting for you to say that.

287
00:14:27,160 --> 00:14:27,950
Bao.

288
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:28,950
Don't worry.

