to your wishes.

302
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,430
The road is right in front of you now.

303
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,110
You choose.

304
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,710
I won't.

305
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:11,150
I still have time

306
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,470
for our bet.

307
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:13,910
In the last month,

308
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:14,910
