310
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,590
Am I still your grandpa?

311
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,710
Are you still a Li?

312
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,190
Will you take over the family business?

313
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,470
I'm full.

314
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,390
What are you going to do?

315
00:15:25,920 --> 00:15:26,950
To become a nun in a temple.

316
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:27,870
Come back here.

317
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:35,470
Uncle,

318
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,710
